    .bg--off-white.py2
      %section#accommodation.measure.p2
        %h3 Accommodation 🏠
        %p
          We've booked a number of cribs for our guests to stay in, and there is a camping ground quite close by.
        %p
          If you need help finding accommodation please let us know when you
          %a{href: "https://goo.gl/forms/6uCqSjKJXH0FaDE72"} RSVP.
        %p
          If you are looking around for a place to stay, we recommend searching for something in Kaka Point or around Balclutha.
        %p
          We'll be providing a bus to get people back to their beds at the end of the night.

    %section#programme.measure.p2
      %h3 Programme
      %h4 Friday the 5th
      %p
        We'll be setting up the venue, and having a 🐟+🍟 dinner that evening.
      %h4 Saturday the 6th &mdash; the big day!
      %p
        3:00 pm &mdash; Arrive at Port Molyenux School.
        %br
        3:30pm &mdash; Ceremony.
        %br
        4:00pm &mdash; Drinks, Nibbles, Beach activities!
        %br
        6:00pm &mdash; Dinner followed by speeches, and partying until midnight.
      %h4 Sunday the 7th
      %p
        10:00am &mdash; Brunch at Port Molyneux.
        On Sunday we'll have a brunch at the venue, which is over the road from the beach, so if it's nice we might have a beach picnic style thing.

